e practical problems for your opponents. If your opponent is well prepared and also is strong in endgames, then the game will end in a draw, but from my experience, I can tell that most of the time, White can get a pleasant pressure, with chances to win. Don't forget that not all of our opponents will be ready to defend for many hours a slightly worse endgame.} *

